Custom video player

Step-1 : Start.
Step-2 : Take one video and store in your local.
step-3 : If user click on video it will pause and play.
step-4 :  if user click on play button it will play
step-5 : if user click on stop button it will stop the video.
step-6 : if user click on progress bar the video will play where the user wants to start the video.
step-7 : we can also show the video duration .
